    <h2>What is Daily Journal?</h2>     
    </div>  
    <div class="col-sm-12 col-md-12">      
      <p>Daily Journal is an application that aims to provide users with an online platform where they can store their thoughts and ideas. 
        It was built with an Express server, MongoDB for the NoSQL database, and EJS as the view engine. With the help of NodeJS, PassportJS,
        and a few other Node packages, I was also able to salt and hash user information. This application will eventually serve as a place
        for me to test various security methods, making this application as secure as possible. 
      </p>      
    </div>  
  </div>

